Both mmiotrace.h and insn-eval.h define various MMIO_ enum constants.
Rename the insn ones to have a INSN_ prefix, so that the headers can be
used from the same source file.

Signed-off-by: Jason A. Donenfeld <Jason@zx2c4.com>
---
I sent this already as a separate patch that I'm hoping can land in 6.2
as a fix, and then I can rebase this series on Linus' tree after that
lands: https://lore.kernel.org/lkml/20221214203454.337299-1-Jason@zx2c4.com/

